{"tid":508052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(好撚痛)掃帚插穿陰囊拮到心口 醫生再由胸拔出好恐怖","createTime":"2017-12-24T00:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T01:29:11.000Z","uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6d04414a9853e6ced5e7803b355ebaee84f4c643","tid":508052,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"巴西發生一宗駭人案件，一名男子為了躲避警察，翻牆跳入一戶住宅，怎料落地位置剛好有一把掃帚，結果柄身木棍從他陰囊插入，穿過腹部再從胸口穿出，情狀恐怖。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁「Cidade Nova &ndash; Ananindeua/Par&aacute;」日前分享這宗事件，地點相信是在巴西東北部大城市貝倫。專頁的上載了該名男子之後動手術的片段，同樣十分駭人。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，醫生拉開男子的陰囊，把掃帚木棍由下方往上推，讓木棍慢慢從胸部整支退出來，看著都感到毛骨悚然。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞《詩華日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171224/57617744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171224%2F57617744&d=puiSddp9Vo3i8vVDNE0kXTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=52dd3a3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171224%2F57617744&h=09facbc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171224/57617744</a>"},{"pid":"1eaccc258dee64758d54dade53735191556ad0bb","tid":508052,"uid":24570,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0741aecf17485256c76f055ccff80fca34d70cd","tid":508052,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:30:18.000Z","msg":"咁都死唔去"},{"pid":"23d0357cd6a82e523838cd441ba4f36d847d08f9","tid":508052,"uid":142725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:31:34.000Z","msg":"諗都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220d9d8b07951bc26a638225ab897f8557de1c88","tid":508052,"uid":159775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12